733370f-c.title: Thanksgiving ragamuffins, No.61-63.
733370f-c.text:
(1)
Thanksgiving Ragamuffins, 1933, No. 61, on the Ioof of the
amall building in Central Park next to the Columbus Circle
entrance. The woman on the bench is looking up at them with
possibly a touch of apprehension. The scene is the same as
that of No. 60.
Novomber 30, 1933.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
No. 62. The same, another view.
November 30, 1933.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(3)
No. 63. The same two girls, on 61st Street near Columbus
Avenue. They're boys, of course.
November 30, 1933.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
